name: Brooke Shields (80s/90s)
description:
Brooke Shields is an American actress and model.

This TI has been updated! Please check the "About this version" section below.

If you get saturated results, remember that you can reduce the embedding's weight in your prompt! Try something like "(brshields:0.99)", see if the pics look better.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
I wasn't happy with some recurring wrinkles that appeared on her eyebrow, even if sometimes they were barely noticeable, so I decided to re-train from scratch. The new version seems to have solved that issue, and I think is probably (at least) as accurate as the previous one.

Do check both versions, though! I guess some people might prefer the previous one, even if Brooke looks a bit older with it.
